when you decide you don't want them.

267
00:23:22,840 --> 00:23:24,319
They already hate us in that store.

268
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:25,799
I forgot to look.

269
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:28,997
- Now, were they on sale?
- Of course they were on sale.

270
00:23:29,120 --> 00:23:31,509
It's 100 degrees outside
and they're long-sleeved.

271
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:34,478
Well, I want my arms covered.

272
00:23:36,280 --> 00:23:38,874
I'm gonna get you
some salve for your face.

273
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:41,753
No, it's fine.
Listen, Doll, I gotta get back to work.

274
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,598
Do you want me to put these
in your closet for you?

275
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:47,349
Yeah. Don't I have a denim blouse?

276
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:49,072
