that deal on the concrete.

283
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:18,628
You'll get it.

284
00:24:18,760 --> 00:24:21,638
Oh, a Frank Bryant
from Mississippi called.

285
00:24:37,280 --> 00:24:39,191
Go on, doggy. Go on!

286
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:41,839
Shoo, dog! Kyah!

287
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,478
Don't you got a home?

288
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:46,874
Ah, crap.

289
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:50,271
Are you mean?
