515
00:43:07,760 --> 00:43:09,159
Yeah, I was a Girl Scout.

516
00:43:09,280 --> 00:43:10,998
- I think I see one.
- Where?

517
00:43:11,120 --> 00:43:12,155
Shine the light, shine the light over here.

518
00:43:12,280 --> 00:43:14,032
Gig him. Get him!

519
00:43:14,160 --> 00:43:16,720
Get him! Yeah, there he is.

520
00:43:16,840 --> 00:43:18,114
- Oh, my God!
- Good job.

521
00:43:18,280 --> 00:43:19,793
Ohh! Oh!

522
00:43:19,960 --> 00:43:21,791
- Aah! Quit it, quit it!
